task.summary: Teacher Summary page and roll call fragment image update
1. Added new layout for ChildSelection activity.
1. Added new layout for ChildSelection activity and associated java codes.
1. Some icons are changed in syllabus, event etc fragments. 2. Some images are added to drawable folder.

1. Added lesson plan view fragment i.e. list of lesson plans. 2. Added lesson plan add fragment i.e create lesson plans. 3. In view lesson plan page added delete and assign functionalities for multiple selection. 4. Added single page of each lesson plan. 5. Added edit and delete functionalities in single page of lesson plan. 6. For editing user is redirect to a new page. 7. Some activities are added in menifest file. 8. Added layouts and associated graphics for each view.
1. Some view related issues are fixed in Lesson Plan for both layouts and associated java classes.
